ting it back in her bag. &quot;I&#039;ll think of something for that one. Anyway, it&#039;s late. I should be heading home.&quot; Standing up, she stretches her muscular body for a moment.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417772554";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff1a1a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14177725467";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#940000";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1134831;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1134831";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:13:"VincentShadow";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Alraune";s:4:"text";s:196:"/me takes a moment to take her body in. Yum. &quot;Damn. Well I&#039;ll see you again soon, then. We can hang out some time. Maybe burn something down.&quot; It wasn&#039;t clear if he was joking.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417772604";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#767676";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14177726353";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff2464";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1134833;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1134833";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Alraune";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"112";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"VincentShadow";s:4:"text";s:305:"&quot;Up to you,&quot; she shrugs. &quot;I generally prefer being alone. But a fire does sound nice on a cold night like tonight.&quot; She nods to the stallion and then turns and begins picking her way through the rubble towards town. She doesn&#039;t go as fast as she could, in case he had more to say.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417772788";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff1a1a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14177727813";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#940000";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1134835;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1134835";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:13:"VincentShadow";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Alraune";s:4: