ing. She&#039;d totally have to tell Scarlet about that. And Bastille too. She&#039;d used &#039;the swagger&#039;. hehe. Vincent was an interesting pony. Certainly a long shot from his father. Could she trust him though? She had the feeling that the closer he was to somepony, the less he used his talent. However, that could backfire. And what did it mean that he hadn&#039;t lied to her in that whole conversation? Well, not .. a lot anyway. Still, this was one more thing on her mind and that wasn&#039;t a happy thing, but this was a fun thing so that helped.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417773304";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff1a1a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14177732967";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#940000";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1134848;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1134848";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Alraune";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"112";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"VincentShadow";s:4:"text";s:93:"((  it was one more thing on her mind and having one more thing wasn&#039;t a happy thing. ))";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417773371";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ff1a1a";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14177733640";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#940000";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1134849;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1134849";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:13:"VincentShadow";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Alraune";s:4:"text";s:17:"[[I understood.]]";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417773383";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#767676";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14177734140";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff2464";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1134850;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1134850";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Alraune";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"112";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"VincentShadow";s:4:"text";s:16:"((  &